Heading to Scottsdale for your BACH? You can book a class with them on the BACH app!

node.text:
🎉 $500 GIVEAWAY 🎉 That's right—we’re giving away $500 in BACH Bucks to one lucky party to use for any experience in the BACH app! From party buses to private chefs to bouncy castles to cabana boys, the BACH app has everything you've dreamed of for the perfect bachelorette weekend.

Here’s all you have to do to enter:

1️⃣ Like this post
2️⃣ Tag your besties in the comments
3️⃣ Enter using the swipe up link in our Instagram Story
⭐ 20 BONUS points if you have a party started in the BACH app! 💖 (enter the contest with the same email address you use for the BACH app)

Hurry! Enter by Monday, August 23rd. Winner will be selected at random and announced on August 24th. Good luck! 🎉

#girlsweekend #bacheloretteparty #bachelorettethemes #bachelorette #bacheloretteweekend #bridetobe #maidofhonor #gettingmarried
